[FILE:312:descriptions/desc.primary]
libsodium is a library for network communication, encryption, decryption,
signatures, etc.

libsodium is a portable, cross-compilable, installable, packageable,
API-compatible version of NaCl(security/nacl).  NaCl's goal is to provide
all of the core operations needed to build higher-level cryptographic
tools.


